0 场，涉及艺人超百人，上海、广州、北京、南京、成都等城市都是举办演唱会场次位居前列的热门城市。 而诸如周杰伦等的巨星演唱会，也被网友称为「行走的 GDP」，到过的地方都将掀起一轮「消费热」。演唱会市场的持续火爆，释放出巨大文旅消费能量，亦成为推动各地消费回暖的重要引擎。四天「赚」9.76 亿元，周杰伦演唱会变海口文旅复苏「流量密码」 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-9327f0cef12613facb34cb345db61655_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "32 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/610636669"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I6PeIur7ZwqtZEAMaCDk3OTc3ODgwINXSmKUGMAA4ogJAFHIJNjEwNjM2NjY5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1688782837.468314", "card_id": "Q_610138398", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 95}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "明明梅西的天赋、技术和荣誉都远超小罗，为什么大众认知中还是小罗的足球天赋更高？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a485dd38fd750abd154bb93e784f4d1c_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/610138398"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I6PeIur7ZwqtZEAMaCDk3ODY3MTA0IMP8iqUGMAA4kwFAFXIJNjEwMTM4Mzk4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1688782837.468673", "card_id": "Q_610584886", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么英语要专门创造一个单词来形容把人扔出窗外？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/610584886"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I6PeIur7ZwqtZEAMaCDk3OTY2MzY4IN2olqUGMAA4V0AWcgk2MTA1ODQ4ODZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "st